events.text:
For someone responsible for life itself, you'd think I'm talented enough to keep a plant. 
I'm not. 
I think it's an act of rebellion from plants though, they don't want help growing. Like a teenage human.
Or you're simply bad at keeping attention to things at a personal level.
Sure, if it's any consolation, you and Owlnu seem to have the same hobby for finding frivolous things that are a good excuse to procrastinate.
